        <sponsor name-id="S305">Mr. Isakson</sponsor> (for himself and <cosponsor name-id="S290">Mr. Chambliss</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSEG00">Committee on Energy and Natural Resources</committee-name>
